ZH: 卿卿我我的爱情是永恒的。
EN: Our love is eternal.

ZH: 他们卿卿我我地牵着手漫步在河边。
EN: They walked hand in hand by the river.

ZH: 卿卿我我的关系越来越深。
EN: Our relationship is getting deeper and deeper.

ZH: 他们卿卿我我地聊了一整夜。
EN: They chatted all night long.

ZH: 卿卿我我的婚礼将在下个月举行。
EN: Our wedding will be held next month.

ZH: 我们卿卿我我地共度每一个周末。
EN: We spend every weekend together.

ZH: 卿卿我我地在阳光下享受彼此的陪伴。
EN: We enjoy each other's company under the sunlight.

ZH: 他们卿卿我我地在海边浪漫约会。
EN: They had a romantic date by the sea.

ZH: 我们卿卿我我地慢慢长大。
EN: We grow up together.

ZH: 卿卿我我的友谊永不磨灭。
EN: Our friendship will never fade.

